trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class provides a hierarchical menu Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>klassen inneholder en hierarkisk meny server webkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning koden kildekode som beskriver de tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to markup and added to the existing markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup og legges til eksisterende markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The MenuDesigner class provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> controls in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuDesigner gir støtte for utforming for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>Kontroller i en visuelle utformeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.ActionLists%2A> property returns a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> object, which typically contains an object that is derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> class for each level in the inheritance tree of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.ActionLists%2A>returnerer en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>objektet, som vanligvis inneholder et objekt som er avledet av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>klasse for hvert nivå i treet arving av designer.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.ActionLists%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property returns a collection of formatting schemes for display in the **Auto Format** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>egenskapen returnerer en samling av formatering skjemaene for visning i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property returns a collection of template groups for the templates of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>egenskapen returnerer en samling av malen grupper for malene for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property always returns `true`, indicating that the designer creates a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>egenskapen returnerer alltid `true`, som angir at det opprettes en midlertidig kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The MenuDesigner class methods provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.Initialize%2A> method prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Metodene MenuDesigner klassen inneholder følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.Initialize%2A>metoden Klargjør utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method returns the markup that is used to render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> at design time.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden returnerer markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A> method gets the markup that renders a placeholder for the associated control at design time when no markup is otherwise available.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A>Metoden henter markup som gjengir en plassholder for den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen når ingen markup ellers er tilgjengelig.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A> method provides the markup that renders the associated control at design time when an error has occurred.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden gir markup som gjengir den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen når det har oppstått en feil.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.DataBind%2A> method binds the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control to the design-time data source.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.DataBind%2A>Metoden binding den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen datakilden utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.DataBind%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetSampleDataSource%2A> method constructs a sample data source that can be used at design time for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetSampleDataSource%2A>metoden bygger en datakilde i eksemplet som kan brukes på utformingstidspunktet for den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.GetSampleDataSource%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll eller en kopi av kontrollen på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Gets the designer action list collection for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter designer handlingen liste-samlingen for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The ActionLists property creates a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> object for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> class, adds it to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> that is obtained from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControlDesigner.ActionLists%2A> base property, and then returns the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ActionLists oppretter en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekt den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>klasse, legger den til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>som er hentet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControlDesigner.ActionLists%2A>basere egenskapen, og returnerer <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControlDesigner.ActionLists%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of predefined formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Henter samling av forhåndsdefinerte oppsett skal vises i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>objektet fylles ut fra forhåndsdefinerte intern konstanter.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> that contains the predefined schemes for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> som inneholder de forhåndsdefinerte skjemaene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Tilknyttede kontrollen bindes til datakilden utformingen.

trans-unit.source: If one of the following conditions is true, the DataBind method clears the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A> property, and then calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControlDesigner.DataBind%2A> base method: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControl.DataSourceID%2A> property is not `null` or an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Hvis én av følgende betingelser er oppfylt, metoden Databinde tømmes den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A>egenskapen og kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControlDesigner.DataBind%2A>basere metoden: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControl.DataSourceID%2A>egenskapen er ikke `null` eller en tom streng ("").</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControl.DataSourceID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.HierarchicalDataBoundControlDesigner.DataBind%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.Items%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataBoundControl.DataSource%2A> property is not `null`.

trans-unit.source: The `dataBoundControl` parameter is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control that is associated with this designer or a copy of that control.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.DataBind%2A> method to bind the design-time data source to the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control, and then the GetDesignTimeHtml calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.GetDesignModeState%2A> method to cause the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control to generate its static-view and dynamic-view markup.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall GetDesignTimeHtml den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.DataBind%2A>metode til å binde utformingen datakilden til den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen, og deretter GetDesignTimeHtml kall den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.GetDesignModeState%2A>metoden vil føre til at den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen til å generere statiske visning og dynamiske visning kodene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.GetDesignModeState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner.DataBind%2A>

trans-unit.source: The GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml method generates the markup for a placeholder that specifies the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control name and a message instructing you to use the collection editor to add items.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml genererer koden for en plassholder som angir den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollerer navn og en melding om du skal bruke redigeringsprogrammet samlingen til å legge til elementer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.target: Metoden GetErrorDesignTimeHtml genererer markup som gjengir den feil utformingen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen som plassholder som inneholder navnet på den kontrollnavnet og meldinger som beskriver problemet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.target: Eksemplet datakilden som er laget av metoden GetSampleDataSource har flere roten menyelementer med tom baner.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups for the templates of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper for malene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property gets a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> object from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> base property.
trans-unit.target: TemplateGroups egenskapen henter en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>objektet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>basere egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: It then adds to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> object named "`ItemTemplates`" that contains two <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> objects named "StaticItemTemplate" and "DynamicItemTemplate".
trans-unit.target: Deretter legges til i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekt med navnet "`ItemTemplates`" som inneholder to <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition>objekter med navnet "StaticItemTemplate" og "DynamicItemTemplate".</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property returns this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> to the caller.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups returnerer dette <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>til oppkalleren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> containing an element for each template in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> som inneholder et element for hver mal i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a copy of the associated control or use the control itself to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en kopi av den tilknyttede kontrollen eller bruke selve kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: Because the UsePreviewControl property is always `true`, the designer uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that contains a copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Fordi egenskapen UsePreviewControl alltid `true`, designer bruker en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>kontroll som inneholder en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control does not affect any persistence for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>kontrollen påvirker ikke noen utholdenhet for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: If the UsePreviewControl property has been overridden to return `false`, the designer uses the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> object itself to generate the design-time markup, and design-time changes to the control are persisted to the page markup source.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen UsePreviewControl er overstyrt for å returnere `false`, designer bruker den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>selve å generere utformingen markup, og endre utformingen kontrollen objektet er beholdt i siden markup kilden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>
